  "_authoring": "PLACEHOLDER content (ADR-012 stretch). Pedagogically coherent with the L4 transfer bank (seed_data/transfer_items.json) and the L4 KCs; every truthTable is computed via @polymath/booleans so loadLesson(4) cannot throw. De Morgan's law is the payoff: NOT(A AND B) = (NOT A) OR (NOT B) and NOT(A OR B) = (NOT A) AND (NOT B). The trap items (l4-*-trap) carry a deliberately-constructed halfway-misconception form whose near-miss output column is authored into lessons/4/misconceptions.json; the misconception detector names it in the hint. Final wording/sequencing across the 4 tiers is Keith's pedagogical authoring (~1 day, see the spec's Manual setup).",
